OL,3,CMan arrested over NI police station
OL,4,Cbomb attack charged
OL,6,FA 66-year-old man arrested over a bomb
OL,7,Fattack on Dunmurry Police Station has
OL,8,Fbeen charged.
OL,10,FThe man was arrested on Tuesday under
OL,11,Fthe Terrorism Act, and taken to
OL,12,FMusgrave Serious Crime Suite for
OL,13,Fquestioning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
