PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777727463
OL,3,CMan arrested over NI police station
OL,4,Cbomb attack charged
OL,6,FHe has been charged with a number of
OL,7,Foffences, including attempted murder,
OL,8,Fpossessing explosives with intent to
OL,9,Fendanger life or cause serious injury
OL,10,Fto property, causing an explosion
OL,11,Flikely to endanger life or cause
OL,12,Fserious injury to property, possession
OL,13,Fof articles for use in terrorism and
OL,14,Fhijacking by compelling person to act.
OL,16,FHe is expected to appear before
OL,17,FLisburn Magistrates' Court on
OL,18,FSaturday, 2nd May.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
