OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777727463
OL,3,CMan arrested over NI police station
OL,4,Cbomb attack charged
OL,6,FAs is usual procedure, all charges
OL,7,Fwill be reviewed by the Public
OL,8,FProsecution Service.
OL,10,FOn Saturday a male delivery driver was
OL,11,Fhijacked in the Twinbrook area of west
OL,12,FBelfast.
OL,14,FA device was placed inside the vehicle
OL,15,Fand he was ordered to drive to
OL,16,FDunmurry police station.
OL,18,FThe car exploded outside the station
OL,19,Fas people were being evacuated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
